  (text "Gate drive: 3.3V logic from PCA9685\nVgs(th) max = 1.45V — fully enhanced at 3.3V\nId max = 4A, motor draw = 80mA typical\nFlyback diode (1N4148WS) must be placed within 10mm of motor terminals"
