  (text "Net names:\n  PWM_IN  — PCA9685 channel output (3.3V PWM, 200Hz)\n  GATE    — MOSFET gate after 220R\n  DRAIN   — MOSFET drain = Motor negative terminal\n  +3V     — 3.0V motor supply rail\n  GND     — common ground (star point)"
